{"tid":1043563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]第一身經歷廢中衝出馬路撞我","createTime":"2019-03-02T11:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T14:06:45.000Z","uid":164634,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5107936baf92eee29b97a6050541749e3cefc4ff","tid":1043563,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"件事啱啱發生<br />\n<br />\n頭先係灣仔太和街轉入灣仔道<br />\n果條街好多街市豬肉菜檔<br />\n平時都有多人行出馬路<br />\n所以都一定開住大燈開到十幾慢行<br />\n<br />\n明明已經同前面啲人keep住五米距離<br />\n忽然有件廢中一眼都唔望就向前衝落馬路<br />\n我honk左一下<br />\n佢就撞埋黎<br />\n過程係一兩秒內發生<br />\n雖然冇聲但應該有同車身接觸<br />\n我都冇打算落車 因為應該唔會嚴重<br />\n<br />\n我O撚左望住佢 佢又O撚左望住我<br />\n我都明係街市<br />\n咁你過馬路都望兩眼先啦 車路黎架嘛<br />\n<br />\n佢仲唔份氣從後影9我<br />\n可能又要放上fb作個故仔公審我<br />\n而家啲廢中堅惡<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有冇遇過哩啲情況？"},{"pid":"a580f32bbd1a5ebd8e89759510f5c1d48c462275","tid":1043563,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"放車cam上來等連登鍵盤戰士討伐佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb28bb6d917cecfbf740edbfcb66921527fba43","tid":1043563,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"你現在身在於: 創意台"},{"pid":"228f5a23f95be1e70f7ba0ff09a381699e07a1df","tid":1043563,"uid":189911,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"我睇標題睇到中出馬路，心諗乜鳩嘢"},{"pid":"4a7bfa73dd4f8023c930262cda8f26ab11d53ba7","tid":1043563,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"a580f32bbd1a5ebd8e89759510f5c1d48c462275","tid":1043563,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"放車cam上來等連登鍵盤戰士討伐佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"冇裝cam<br />\n反正我唔係話想公審佢<br />\n有咩謂"},{"pid":"4e07bd50f3f61ef1a183dd3715aeded3b449e361","tid":1043563,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb28bb6d9